title: Trinidad And Tobago Producer Prices
description: Producer Prices in Trinidad And Tobago increased to 629.10 points in the second quarter of 2022 from 628.60 points in the first quarter of 2022. Producer Prices in Trinidad And Tobago averaged 477.89 points from 1995 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 629.10 points in the second quarter of 2022 and a record low of 332.20 points in the third quarter of 1995. This page provides - Trinidad And Tobago Producer Prices- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Central Bank of Trinidad and Tobago
